Oscar Mayer and Co Inc, a unit ofPhilip Morris Cos Inc, said it will redeem all of itsoutstanding 7.85 pct debentures due January 15, 1996 on April30, 1987, at 1,014.50 dlrs plus accrued interest for each 1,000dlrs prinicpal amount.    A notice of redemption will be mailed to noteholders March27, it said. Reuter&#3;